# PWA + Service Worker

- Service worker source lives in `src/workers/`; registration lives only in `src/sw/register.ts`.
- Never cache POST, PUT, PATCH, or DELETE responses.
- Use IndexedDB via Dexie for game saves; never localStorage.
- E2E offline tests must use Playwright `context.setOffline(true)`.
- Keep manifest installable and run Lighthouse PWA audits in CI.
